## Production Checklist

- [ ] Set `DEBUG=false` in `.env`
- [ ] Use secrets manager (AWS Secrets Manager, Vault) instead of `.env`
- [ ] Set `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` to your frontend domain
- [ ] Enable structured logging (replace `print` with `logging`)
- [ ] Set up monitoring (Prometheus + Grafana, or Datadog)
- [ ] Configure autoscaling on the API service
- [ ] Set up a CI/CD pipeline (see `.github/workflows/`)

